description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Registered Nurse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£16.35 standard hourly rate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£21.26 for nights and Saturday (all day)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£24.53 for Sundays (all day)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£1500 Golden Hello *&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Dean&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for a Registered Nurse to join our 60 bed dedicated neurological care centre, The Dean based at The Winfield Hospital site in Gloucester. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We deliver expert care and rehabilitation for complex neurological conditions.   Our team is currently on an exciting journey to achieve excellence and you can be part of this!  This is a role where you can make a difference every day in a supported environment, where we will value your skills and clinical expertise. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we can offer you: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;£16.35 per hour (plus generous enhancements and additional overtime incentives)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributory pension scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to the Ramsay Academy – genuine opportunities to grow, develop and specialise in your career&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;25 days annual leave plus the opportunity to buy/sell more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible shift options&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private Healthcare and Life Assurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free onsite parking and a subsidised staff restaurant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free uniform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to our employee Discount Programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current NMC registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent clinical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to make decisions and use your initiative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate to deliver excellent care in a rewarding and what can be emotionally challenging environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible and positive attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*T and C&#39;s apply&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like the opportunity to visit us and see and understand the amazing work we do please contact Jane Johnson for an informal chat.   Alternatively apply via Ramsay Careers.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are committed to equality of opportunity for all. This position is subject to an Enhanced DBS check&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We love people with a positive, “can do” attitude who want to make a difference in their work. &quot;Our employees are Ramsay&quot; The skills and commitment of our employees forms the basis for our success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
